<br>
49 pets max = 41st level<br>
51 + Vocerates = 45th level<br>
<br>
So your 51 Earth has 4 levels more of dual weild, block, def / off / double attack / dodge / parry, etc - also has more hp to boot!  (Skills raise applies only if pets skill levels rise per level as players do)<br>
<br>
Also being 4 levels higher means the root will stick more often versus using a 49 pet, and its root does damage so its not a totally wasted cast :P Jabober can kill bixies with root from 50 yards away! Wheee!<br>
<br>
Limpy<br>
<br>
&gt;I don't have any of the focus items for the lvl 51 pets or better.<br>
<br>
Me neither, but you don't have to have them - if you get them you'll most likely turn them in for epic, then use epic pet from then on.<br>
<br>
